WEBVTT

00:01:26.580 --> 00:01:31.179
This pattern will continue until
all 100 of you have gone.

00:01:31.179 --> 00:01:34.462
The words in the lockers that remain
open at the end

00:01:34.462 --> 00:01:38.037
will help you crack the code for the safe.

00:01:38.037 --> 00:01:42.644
Before cousin Thaddeus can even start
down the line,

00:01:42.644 --> 00:01:49.012
you step forward and tell the lawyer
you know which lockers will remain open.

00:01:49.012 --> 00:01:51.366
But how?

00:01:51.366 --> 00:01:54.332
Pause the video now if you want
to figure it out for yourself!

00:01:54.332 --> 00:01:55.421
Answer in: 3

00:01:55.421 --> 00:01:56.577
Answer in: 2

00:01:56.577 --> 00:01:58.248
Answer in: 1

00:01:58.248 --> 00:02:02.151
The key is realizing that the number
of times a locker is touched